sequenceDiagram
    box Planning Team
    participant LD as Leaders (Tech Lead + PDM)
    end

    box Integration & Quality Team (Final Flow)
    participant Sonar as sonar-quality-gate
    participant MCPInt as mcp-integration-tester
    participant VideoRec as test-video-recorder
    participant UnitRev as unit-test-standards-reviewer
    participant Report as quality-report-generator
    end

    %% PHASE 0: Trigger - Final Integration Test
    Note over LD,Report: PHASE 4: Final Integration & Quality Flow

    LD->>Sonar: Trigger final quality & integration validation
    Note right of LD: Inputs from phases 2 & 3:<br/>- Backend (OpenAPI/Swagger)<br/>- Frontend Web (React/Angular)<br/>- Frontend App (Flutter/React Native)

    %% PHASE 1: Sonar Quality Validation
    Note over Sonar,Report: PHASE 1: Quality Validations (Sonar)

    activate Sonar
    Note right of Sonar: Sonar Quality Gate:<br/>- Code quality (bugs, code smells)<br/>- Security (vulnerabilities, hotspots)<br/>- Coverage (unit tests %)<br/>- Duplications<br/>- Maintainability rating<br/>- Reliability rating<br/>- Pass/Fail quality gate
    Sonar->>Sonar: Run analysis (Backend + Frontend)
    Sonar-->>UnitRev: Sonar report (coverage, issues)
    Sonar-->>MCPInt: ✓ Quality gate passed / failed
    deactivate Sonar

    %% PHASE 2: Unit Test Standards Review
    Note over UnitRev: PHASE 2: Unit Test Standards Review

    activate UnitRev
    Note right of UnitRev: Unit Test Standards Review:<br/>- Naming conventions<br/>- Coverage thresholds (>80%)<br/>- Assertion quality<br/>- Test isolation & independence<br/>- Mock/stub usage<br/>- Edge cases coverage<br/>- Alignment with Sonar report
    UnitRev-->>Report: Unit test standards report
    deactivate UnitRev

    %% PHASE 3: MCP Integration Testing + Video Recording
    Note over MCPInt,VideoRec: PHASE 3: MCP Integration Testing & Video Recording

    Sonar->>MCPInt: Proceed with integration tests
    activate MCPInt
    Note right of MCPInt: MCP Integration Testing:<br/>- E2E flows (Backend ↔ Frontend)<br/>- API contract validation<br/>- Cross-module scenarios<br/>- Playwright / Cypress / MCP tools<br/>- Environment parity checks<br/>- Integration test results
    MCPInt->>VideoRec: Request test execution recording
    deactivate MCPInt

    activate VideoRec
    Note right of VideoRec: Test Video Recording (MCP):<br/>- Record E2E test runs<br/>- Record integration scenarios<br/>- Screenshots on failure<br/>- Video per test suite / flow<br/>- Attach to test reports
    VideoRec-->>Report: Test videos + screenshots
    deactivate VideoRec

    MCPInt-->>Report: Integration test results

    %% PHASE 4: Consolidated Report & Delivery
    Note over Report: PHASE 4: Consolidated Quality Report

    activate Report
    Note right of Report: Final Report includes:<br/>- Sonar quality gate result<br/>- Unit test standards review<br/>- Integration test results (MCP)<br/>- Test video recordings<br/>- Coverage & metrics summary<br/>- Go/No-Go recommendation
    Report-->>LD: Final quality report + test videos
    deactivate Report
